.TH SPACEGL_VIEWER 1 "2026-04-19" "SpaceGL @VERSION@" "SpaceGL Manual"
.SH NAME
spacegl_viewer \- SpaceGL galaxy state viewer
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B spacegl_viewer
.RI [ OPTIONS ]
.SH DESCRIPTION
.B spacegl_viewer
is a lightweight viewer for the SpaceGL engine that reads and displays
galaxy state data from shared memory (SHM) produced by
.BR spacegl_server (1).
It provides a terminal-based overview of active ships, entities, and
network statistics without requiring a full 3D rendering context.
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
.B \-\-version
Print version information and exit.
.SH FILES
.TP
.I /usr/bin/spacegl_viewer
Viewer executable.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR spacegl_client (1),
.BR spacegl_server (1),
.BR spacegl_hud (1),
.BR spacegl_diag (1)
